## Language & Pricing Context
- Primary market: Malaysia
- Currency: Malaysian Ringgit (MYR / RM)
- Languages: Bahasa Malaysia (ms), English (en), Mandarin (zh)
- i18n is already integrated in `apps/web-shop` via `LanguageProvider`
